des:
Heidi FM The Hip Hop Dance Station originating from a secret undisclosed location for our underground studio. It's soul rockin' Hip Hop all day and the hottest dance tracks all night to keep the party going. 

You can say:

"Alexa, open Heidi FM"
"Alexa, play Heidi FM"
"Alexa, start Heidi FM"

Please review this skill, or send us an email with your suggestions studio@heidifm.com. Your reviews encourage us to keep making more great skills, thanks!
